Name: Actual Forecast And Budgets
Expression: {[Version].[Version].[Actual],EXCEPT(DRILLDOWNMEMBER({[Version].[Version].[All Forecasts]} , {[Version].[Version].[All Forecasts]} , RECURSIVE) , {[Version].[Version].[All Forecasts]}),EXCEPT(DRILLDOWNMEMBER({[Version].[Version].[All Budgets]} , {[Version].[Version].[All Budgets]} , RECURSIVE) , {[Version].[Version].[All Budgets]})}
